data.description: PRICE DROP! Stunning WATER VIEWS from this 2 bed 1 1/2 bath townhouse in the resort-like community of Waterside at Coquina Key! See picturesque sunrises from the 2nd floor balcony off the master suite & relax in the shade on your fenced back patio while taking in this breathtaking view. Inside is just as stunning with everything upgraded including top of the line ceiling fans, new tile flooring, renovated kitchen with sleek tile backsplash & new appliances, & totally redone bath with overhead showerhead, built-in cabinetry, 2 sinks & vanities plus entry to both the master & hall to share with the 2nd bedroom. The master suite has a contemporary style barn door going into bathroom extension, double closets, plush carpet & balcony. The 1st floor living area features a functional layout with a half bath &  a pass through from the kitchen to the living room serves as a breakfast bar & opens up the home to views of the bay from all main living areas. Hurricane grade windows & doors offer safety. Live the resort lifestyle year round with community features that include a clubhouse, community pool, fishing pier, tennis courts, billiards hall, lending library, full bar, dog park & more! Monthly fee is all inclusive & electric updated 2 years ago. Located right off the bay in the southern tip of St Petersburg close to Downtown, the Boyd Hill Nature Preserve, & the Sunshine Skyway bridge.
